text: Kai Rüder (born 27 August 1971) is a German equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Germany Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Fehmarn
